{"tid":124793,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"上水宵夜天橋","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T21:45:18.000Z","uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68c81970ca12a7836b21ac47bfebc556f0796056","tid":124793,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"賣雲吞果檔係咪冇做？ 五，六年前成日同ex食 幾日前經過搵極都冇"},{"pid":"af0e7804df3b82579d688dad6d599367265f7c80","tid":124793,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"一直好奇點解有人中意<br />\n<br />\n又貴又污糟<br />\n<br />\n係咪食個情懷"},{"pid":"c1dfd87ced4072d877277487c35270057d7f1a8f","tid":124793,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"D小食 貴到可以買個飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2773c0bc41480981a6d59e066e5bf799018eb749","tid":124793,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"鍾意買糖水"},{"pid":"90ae337a5ec9f15c8d1d5d2387d69b3b17bfde93","tid":124793,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:23:08.000Z","msg":"除左油渣麵其他都愈做愈衰"},{"pid":"ea20c50eb9f928d673c371da5d8b6eae5c179408","tid":124793,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直好奇點解有人中意<br />\n<br />\n又貴又污糟<br />\n<br />\n係咪食個情懷</blockquote>"},{"pid":"89f28a8733973e25e7e96460d7fa05b7e69078a7","tid":124793,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直好奇點解有人中意<br />\n<br />\n又貴又污糟<br />\n<br />\n係咪食個情懷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情懷都算係既  而且有特色有風味，好似行花市咁由頭行到尾，再由尾行番頭先決定食乜，好熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方便快捷(火車站旁，d人出完街坐火車番上水可以係個到買埋野食先番屋企，我自己直情住附近，細個成日同爸媽特登落一落去買宵夜番來食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n多選擇(而家少左好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)  開得夜(夜晚12點幾都仲有檔開緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n整體味道不錯(除左某幾檔)<br />\n<br />\n大致上係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可惜而家已經不復再，低質左好多感覺上"},{"pid":"cb6e05b92f0af77b57641eff579587b4ed645241","tid":124793,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直好奇點解有人中意<br />\n<br />\n又貴又污糟<br />\n<br />\n係咪食個情懷</blockquote><br />\n以前住彩園都唔係成日買，又貴又污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班小販搞到條橋污糟邋遢又唔肯執手尾，到領展做野又怕慘講到比人迫害咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要食宵夜寧願行去串燒妹果頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0521a2d6eb95c3fb603e0671649dafd09c6fb6","tid":124793,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一直好奇點解有人中意<br />\n<br />\n又貴又污糟<br />\n<br />\n係咪食個情懷</blockquote><br />\n以前住彩園都唔係成日買，又貴又污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班小販搞到條橋污糟邋遢又唔肯執手尾，到領展做野又扮慘講到比人迫害咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要食宵夜寧願行去串燒妹果頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}